short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Imports the currently displayed page to the inEntertainment application.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
NOTE: This extension is only for users of the inEntertainment application.

This extension is used to transmit project/breakdown information from approved breakdown sites to the inEntertainment application in order for that data to be processed and added to the inEntertainment database.

For a list of the currently supported breakdown sites, visit the inEntertainment web site.
